 This beautiful love tale started in the office! Valerie, who was very much extroverted and full of life became friends with her introverted co-worker, Samuel. What started as two work buddies being cool soon blossomed into so much more. Now the lovely Ghanaian couple is ready for their forever journey. Things have moved from the physics law of attraction to pure chemistry! We’re absolutely drooling over Valerie and Samuel’s steamy pre-wedding shoot and all the chemistry they exude. Valerie gives us the scoop on how this love came to be. You can enjoy it all as you scroll. Take in all the  beauty of their sweet pre-wedding shoot below: <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1305266 lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="https://www.bellanaijaweddings.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Valerie-Samuel-BellaNaija-Weddings5-scaled.jpg" alt="" width="1978" height="2560"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1305266 lazyload jetpack-lazy-image" src="https://i1.wp.com/www.bellanaijaweddings.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Valerie-Samuel-BellaNaija-Weddings5-scaled.jpg?resize=1080%2C1398&#038;ssl=1" alt width="1080" height="1398" data-recalc-dims="1" data-lazy-src="https://i1.wp.com/www.bellanaijaweddings.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Valerie-Samuel-BellaNaija-Weddings5-scaled.jpg?resize=1080%2C1398&amp;is-pending-load=1#038;ssl=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7"><noscript><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1305266 lazyload" src="https://i1.wp.com/www.bellanaijaweddings.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Valerie-Samuel-BellaNaija-Weddings5-scaled.jpg?resize=1080%2C1398&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="1080" height="1398"  data-recalc-dims="1"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1305267 lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-sr